{"0d19900d-8f3e-4ccb-8f63-9b233f9d866a": {"uid": "0d19900d-8f3e-4ccb-8f63-9b233f9d866a", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*0.1 前言", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "a7f3d083-940b-4fa0-a4ff-7c7659c6503c": {"uid": "a7f3d083-940b-4fa0-a4ff-7c7659c6503c", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *本文为示范性的人物事件模板教程，说明文字统一使用空白指令，并在文本开头有个*进行标记", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "3fae13f8-136b-4e8b-beb0-5d25a57fc486": {"uid": "3fae13f8-136b-4e8b-beb0-5d25a57fc486", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *在进行本教程前，请先完成[人物口上模板教程]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "86a90a64-bbc8-4818-b541-88e4019563e2": {"uid": "86a90a64-bbc8-4818-b541-88e4019563e2", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "54a51970-dae4-4151-9892-c5bd78984c57": {"uid": "54a51970-dae4-4151-9892-c5bd78984c57", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*1.1 结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "69cbf047-4e00-4a7d-abb4-ed3bd6e6b0c1": {"uid": "69cbf047-4e00-4a7d-abb4-ed3bd6e6b0c1", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  * 事件 和 口上 的区别就是，事件就是多了[结算]的口上，其他完全一致", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "a6e283e4-0ba2-4974-b9a4-f7b667753c8e": {"uid": "a6e283e4-0ba2-4974-b9a4-f7b667753c8e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *在游戏中进行指令时，你可以看到除了显示文本之外，还会有若干数值上的变化", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "da9461ee-a5cb-4a49-862b-a3b639c21520": {"uid": "da9461ee-a5cb-4a49-862b-a3b639c21520", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *这些数值上的变化就是结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "a1227454-3c36-4c7b-821e-950b4e5b33dc": {"uid": "a1227454-3c36-4c7b-821e-950b4e5b33dc", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *比方说，下方的示例事件，就是调整[聊天]指令的结算，有兴趣可以改完角色id进游戏测试一下", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "ce1e7b19-10f8-4c07-b0e2-b6905ac0c32c": {"uid": "ce1e7b19-10f8-4c07-b0e2-b6905ac0c32c", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "这是聊天指令的测试事件，类型为跳过指令，前提为空，结算为交互对象+1音乐经验", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"285": 1}}, "262c8f96-0db4-4240-bd66-8d893134e55e": {"uid": "262c8f96-0db4-4240-bd66-8d893134e55e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *和前提一样，结算也有[整体修改]和[综合数值结算]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "97fb86a6-d63b-46fe-bbee-9b120772dca4": {"uid": "97fb86a6-d63b-46fe-bbee-9b120772dca4", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *两者的用法和[口上教程]里基本一致，在此不再赘述", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "f3cba4d5-c502-4f91-a9d8-fd5435df451a": {"uid": "f3cba4d5-c502-4f91-a9d8-fd5435df451a", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *需要注意的是，如果不需要结算的话，结算栏也不能空着，请使用[什么都没有的空结算]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "392c5564-59b3-4954-96b4-a1123ea5eada": {"uid": "392c5564-59b3-4954-96b4-a1123ea5eada", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "f42088fa-01ce-4945-bc8b-d2067de6a056": {"uid": "f42088fa-01ce-4945-bc8b-d2067de6a056", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*1.2 事件触发时机", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "c50c6034-34ec-4f08-b3b2-a4c09bf27ef6": {"uid": "c50c6034-34ec-4f08-b3b2-a4c09bf27ef6", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *事件有三种触发时机可以选择", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "12ca331d-fd15-439b-b3b9-f1025189d00b": {"uid": "12ca331d-fd15-439b-b3b9-f1025189d00b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *事件先指令后->[指令后置]、事件代替指令触发->[跳过指令]、指令先事件后->[指令前置]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "28d31111-2cfd-4c5e-bb4d-a4ecbe55c56f": {"uid": "28d31111-2cfd-4c5e-bb4d-a4ecbe55c56f", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *最常使用的是，用事件代替指令，也就是[跳过指令]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "35e82360-af8f-460e-806c-b219375dd9db": {"uid": "35e82360-af8f-460e-806c-b219375dd9db", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *当你需要修改一个指令的结算时，那就跳过它，自己写结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "11c32571-5836-447a-9bf8-abffcdac38ee": {"uid": "11c32571-5836-447a-9bf8-abffcdac38ee", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *以下是一个例子，前提已经给出，请按照说明文字来加上对应的结算吧", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "2bd784d8-fe3d-4e83-b2aa-2a4197ff9d14": {"uid": "2bd784d8-fe3d-4e83-b2aa-2a4197ff9d14", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "这是聊天指令的测试事件，类型为跳过指令\\n前提为：NPC触发，交互对象是玩家，自己有4级陷落，该地点仅有自己和玩家\\n结算为：自己增加5对话经验(综合数值结算)，自己增加少量欲情(整体分类结算)", "premise": {"self_fall_4": 1, "place_10": 1, "sys_1": 1, "sys_4": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "d7d74364-36f3-4394-aad1-1a492710c14b": {"uid": "d7d74364-36f3-4394-aad1-1a492710c14b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *但在一些特殊情况下，你可能会想要在指令正常触发的同时，也触发事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "d036c218-eac3-4abb-8f2a-d3981c54688e": {"uid": "d036c218-eac3-4abb-8f2a-d3981c54688e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *比方说在游戏中有这么一个事件，欲求不满的NPC进到房间里推倒了玩家", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "3d9901f7-05a0-407a-a6cf-a0b2fd4ec581": {"uid": "3d9901f7-05a0-407a-a6cf-a0b2fd4ec581", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *这个事件的触发指令是NPC的移动，触发时间呢？显然是在移动之后", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "bd2de95b-0bc3-4237-983f-f649b2393e47": {"uid": "bd2de95b-0bc3-4237-983f-f649b2393e47", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *所以我们需要的是，先结算移动指令，抵达了房间之后再结算推倒事件，指令在前事件在后，即[指令前置]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "027c3da1-0e0b-44a0-b10b-32d84e7b445e": {"uid": "027c3da1-0e0b-44a0-b10b-32d84e7b445e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *具体的事件条目就是下面这个↓", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "88ee6490-b213-470c-8feb-55190c58471d": {"uid": "88ee6490-b213-470c-8feb-55190c58471d", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "1", "start": 0, "type": 1, "text": "{Name}最近有些欲求不满，看到房间里四下无人，终于抑制不住自己的冲动，一边解开衣服一边向{PlayerName}扑了过来", "premise": {"place_0": 1, "sys_1": 1, "place_10": 1, "desire_point_ge_80": 1, "CVP_A1_G_GE_3": 1, "pl_action_not_move": 1, "place_furniture_3": 1, "self_and_target_hp_ge_70": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"10002": 1, "10005": 1, "10001": 1}}, "480a383d-756d-4238-8046-25746b5d8c9b": {"uid": "480a383d-756d-4238-8046-25746b5d8c9b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *同理，当你需要先触发事件，再触发指令时，就使用[指令后置]吧！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "c54477c4-8f94-4b6d-81ef-0e097746dc7b": {"uid": "c54477c4-8f94-4b6d-81ef-0e097746dc7b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "1b06a02a-367e-41c3-bf3f-256223c91e8b": {"uid": "1b06a02a-367e-41c3-bf3f-256223c91e8b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*1.3 综合指令结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b6dbb710-e602-4082-b9c1-d4b251cac4ad": {"uid": "b6dbb710-e602-4082-b9c1-d4b251cac4ad", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *顾名思义，是用来直接执行一个指令的结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "57cb6dd3-f1dc-4bd4-a228-cd6d1b1e401d": {"uid": "57cb6dd3-f1dc-4bd4-a228-cd6d1b1e401d", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *可以调用游戏中的大部分指令，包括有地点或者属性限制解锁的指令也可以无视限制强行触发", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "d36e1623-1408-4f9f-94da-4d4ae7a59c03": {"uid": "d36e1623-1408-4f9f-94da-4d4ae7a59c03", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *限于技术因素，目前还只支持[玩家对自己]或[玩家对交互对象]来调用指令", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "fc89978d-0bb9-42d6-a555-fe53ca5f2890": {"uid": "fc89978d-0bb9-42d6-a555-fe53ca5f2890", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *同样限于技术因素，目前也无法调用[移动]指令来移动到地图的某个位置", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b7b08469-19fc-48f2-af6d-8925b31dad46": {"uid": "b7b08469-19fc-48f2-af6d-8925b31dad46", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *以下为操作例子，请按照说明添加对应的指令结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "49c66565-dad7-4e6b-909c-7c88f6604cdd": {"uid": "49c66565-dad7-4e6b-909c-7c88f6604cdd", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "301", "start": 0, "type": 1, "text": "这是摸头指令的测试事件，类型为指令前置\\n前提为：玩家触发，交互对象爱情系且≥恋慕\\n结算为：玩家对交互对象进行亲吻(综合指令结算)", "premise": {"sys_0": 1, "love_ge_2": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "3781e459-9cd2-489b-b6c3-d341928851b3": {"uid": "3781e459-9cd2-489b-b6c3-d341928851b3", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "8b7f7761-27b8-4df1-ba3b-03697e760285": {"uid": "8b7f7761-27b8-4df1-ba3b-03697e760285", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*2.1 单次父子事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b28dec79-ee48-4f14-ace5-54001e862481": {"uid": "b28dec79-ee48-4f14-ace5-54001e862481", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *选项与分支！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "03cdf16a-dee5-4fd7-adff-4ac676aafd9a": {"uid": "03cdf16a-dee5-4fd7-adff-4ac676aafd9a", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *事件里不可缺少的就是让玩家进行选择，然后有不同的结果", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "2a5a47fd-a229-4bb7-be51-32113af66578": {"uid": "2a5a47fd-a229-4bb7-be51-32113af66578", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *对于简单的选项事件，也就是只进行一次选择时，可以使用父子事件结算", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "275dd0df-7b42-4582-b99f-10a26de80e4b": {"uid": "275dd0df-7b42-4582-b99f-10a26de80e4b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *首先写父事件，也就是选项之前的内容", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "ad3b65f3-f599-4c04-966c-a7b6ff7ea075": {"uid": "ad3b65f3-f599-4c04-966c-a7b6ff7ea075", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *父事件的结算使用[整体修改]-[系统量_基础]-[开启子选项面板]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "4459a4d2-c5db-4803-9531-c69db7059e66": {"uid": "4459a4d2-c5db-4803-9531-c69db7059e66", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *接着是子事件，也就是每个选项的事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "08473f75-5247-4855-a259-3080554411d5": {"uid": "08473f75-5247-4855-a259-3080554411d5", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *子事件的前提要和父事件一致，并且再多加一个[整体修改]-[系统状态]-[选项的子事件]", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "548e6030-ee18-4fed-9e12-7d24593da770": {"uid": "548e6030-ee18-4fed-9e12-7d24593da770", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *通过以上的父事件结算与子事件前提，两者就建立起了联系", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "48f3140b-eb2b-4176-ba49-ca2d13f05df7": {"uid": "48f3140b-eb2b-4176-ba49-ca2d13f05df7", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *子事件中，需要同时写选项的文本，以及选择后出现的文本，两者用符号|隔开", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "505b186d-061a-47fa-8c48-1202aa607beb": {"uid": "505b186d-061a-47fa-8c48-1202aa607beb", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *以下为参考范例，相信你在游戏中应该也遇到过↓", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "6b39ddda-f2a2-4ca0-8f4f-73ec901e1b41": {"uid": "6b39ddda-f2a2-4ca0-8f4f-73ec901e1b41", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "1", "start": 0, "type": 1, "text": "{TargetSceneName}里现在好像有人，要进去吗", "premise": {"move_to_ladies_only": 1, "sys_0": 1, "place_over_one": 1, "not_move_to_someone_masturebate": 1}, "effect": {"10001": 1}}, "80b20513-336b-475f-8c4d-f1f3c4c6a6d7": {"uid": "80b20513-336b-475f-8c4d-f1f3c4c6a6d7", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "1", "start": 0, "type": 1, "text": "进去|{NickName}被{SrcOneCharaName}很生气地赶出来了", "premise": {"move_to_ladies_only": 1, "sys_0": 1, "place_over_one": 1, "option_son": 1, "not_move_to_someone_masturebate": 1}, "effect": {"23": 1, "24": 1, "761": 1}}, "4ab12512-cd94-45a8-94e7-d398ddea9977": {"uid": "4ab12512-cd94-45a8-94e7-d398ddea9977", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "1", "start": 0, "type": 1, "text": "不进去|{NickName}放弃了打算", "premise": {"move_to_ladies_only": 1, "sys_0": 1, "place_over_one": 1, "option_son": 1, "not_move_to_someone_masturebate": 1}, "effect": {"761": 1}}, "dc930560-2b8b-456a-a9b3-060504e09f02": {"uid": "dc930560-2b8b-456a-a9b3-060504e09f02", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *单次父子事件虽然只有一次选项，但是选项的数量是没有上限的，请尽管使用吧！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "7c62866e-632f-488c-b123-3b8cf7080f35": {"uid": "7c62866e-632f-488c-b123-3b8cf7080f35", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "fd4ecb85-abb2-4114-bfa4-f62dd7eea69d": {"uid": "fd4ecb85-abb2-4114-bfa4-f62dd7eea69d", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*2.2 嵌套父子事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "4ad8d878-a73e-4c82-8e36-e2b785b1ae6b": {"uid": "4ad8d878-a73e-4c82-8e36-e2b785b1ae6b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *复杂的多重选项与分支！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "14a132c5-10e5-47b7-8f1f-b46800cb9923": {"uid": "14a132c5-10e5-47b7-8f1f-b46800cb9923", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *当你需要写一个很庞大的，有相当长一段剧情的CG型演出事件时，单次选项就不够了", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "8cd489bc-ce87-4551-8302-87cf9022c8c8": {"uid": "8cd489bc-ce87-4551-8302-87cf9022c8c8", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *此时我们就需要使用嵌套父子事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "ced9e445-efa7-4f25-b91c-f18ddfff5026": {"uid": "ced9e445-efa7-4f25-b91c-f18ddfff5026", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *先看例子，然后再讲解原理↓", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "955f58a5-70ed-4eef-b7a2-1242293adb76": {"uid": "955f58a5-70ed-4eef-b7a2-1242293adb76", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "嵌套父子事件测试用，父事件A1", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A1_Father|1_E_1": 1}}, "4f0de8b5-60a8-4a8a-8c63-e12add64ee08": {"uid": "4f0de8b5-60a8-4a8a-8c63-e12add64ee08", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "B1|嵌套父子事件测试用，一级子事件B1，为A1的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A1_Father|1_E_2": 1}}, "640b0eaf-5372-4beb-b23b-42845e47afd8": {"uid": "640b0eaf-5372-4beb-b23b-42845e47afd8", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "B2|嵌套父子事件测试用，一级子事件B2，为A1的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A1_Father|1_E_3": 1}}, "0d4206d1-f173-4f6e-8892-bb1c325a2497": {"uid": "0d4206d1-f173-4f6e-8892-bb1c325a2497", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "C1|嵌套父子事件测试用，二级子事件C1，为B1的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_2": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "decf0346-5f9f-471f-bd04-eef0416280a0": {"uid": "decf0346-5f9f-471f-bd04-eef0416280a0", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "C2|嵌套父子事件测试用，二级子事件C2，为B1的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_2": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b6945379-b910-4487-b2fd-e2bd48437ebe": {"uid": "b6945379-b910-4487-b2fd-e2bd48437ebe", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "C3|嵌套父子事件测试用，二级子事件C3，为B2的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_3": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "223ccbe4-b41c-4694-8447-49bb77f86a86": {"uid": "223ccbe4-b41c-4694-8447-49bb77f86a86", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "101", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "C4|嵌套父子事件测试用，二级子事件C4，为B2的子事件", "premise": {"CVP_A1_Son|1_E_3": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "36255358-5bc4-468a-8b30-e6b56260a97d": {"uid": "36255358-5bc4-468a-8b30-e6b56260a97d", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *在这个例子中，选项的树状图逻辑是这样的\\n\\n    A1\\n   /  \\\\n B1    B2\\n /\\    /\\\\nC1 C2 C3 C4", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b92f3974-a82e-401c-ab1c-4666632058d0": {"uid": "b92f3974-a82e-401c-ab1c-4666632058d0", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *A1的结算调用了在1号父子事件中值等于1的事件，也就是B1和B2", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "9ca2f381-7821-4908-a1d3-99852f8f89d6": {"uid": "9ca2f381-7821-4908-a1d3-99852f8f89d6", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *B1的结算调用了在1号父子事件中值等于2的事件，也就是C1和C2", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "43afed88-bff5-4b7d-ba55-272b7b53cbb4": {"uid": "43afed88-bff5-4b7d-ba55-272b7b53cbb4", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *B2的结算调用了在1号父子事件中值等于3的事件，也就是C3和C4", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "97a97577-cf13-4f3c-a79c-119e5a6897be": {"uid": "97a97577-cf13-4f3c-a79c-119e5a6897be", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *你可能要花一段时间来理解这里的逻辑，但只要弄清楚之后还是很简单的", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "0b9cb27a-459d-40d1-842c-c62e9a3c4b78": {"uid": "0b9cb27a-459d-40d1-842c-c62e9a3c4b78", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *利用嵌套父子事件，你可以写出无限长度的复杂事件，来实现你要的丰富演出效果", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "a043c354-74ee-4cf4-bec7-144341e76610": {"uid": "a043c354-74ee-4cf4-bec7-144341e76610", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "0e89160a-f441-4f33-a6c6-c4d0271953ca": {"uid": "0e89160a-f441-4f33-a6c6-c4d0271953ca", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*3.1 口上用flag", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "9d2ca058-27dc-4db5-9ef4-3047a7f9acca": {"uid": "9d2ca058-27dc-4db5-9ef4-3047a7f9acca", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *我要定义自己的游戏数据！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "5b5f170a-7c90-4f42-bf89-265af6e2785c": {"uid": "5b5f170a-7c90-4f42-bf89-265af6e2785c", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *游戏里的数值有很多，但是为了达成一些特殊的效果，需要让口上作者能自己定义和修改某些数值", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b5e3aa2a-1852-4129-83d8-ddff5133dc1b": {"uid": "b5e3aa2a-1852-4129-83d8-ddff5133dc1b", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *比方说，我觉得现在游戏里的4阶段陷落太单薄了，我想做一个有10个阶段的丰富攻略过程", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "07dc342f-b862-4761-bdf4-8aa1a77bab5e": {"uid": "07dc342f-b862-4761-bdf4-8aa1a77bab5e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *再比方说，我想统计角色使用了多少次某个指令，根据使用次数的不同有不同的阶段性事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "cb1b0a95-f82e-478d-bcd3-62245307f7bf": {"uid": "cb1b0a95-f82e-478d-bcd3-62245307f7bf", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *这到了口上作者专用的flag的出场时机了", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "628f141b-61a6-48bd-812a-b761841b2364": {"uid": "628f141b-61a6-48bd-812a-b761841b2364", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *ark为每个角色准备了50个可用的int数值栏位，使用自己定义的数值，可以实现很多游戏里没有的功能", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "f5c5e627-b276-4a18-b200-5012fd25a035": {"uid": "f5c5e627-b276-4a18-b200-5012fd25a035", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *flag的使用很简单，在综合数值结算里修改，在综合数值前提里调用", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "1604b27f-f2c2-47f6-8c47-08d03df8ff4a": {"uid": "1604b27f-f2c2-47f6-8c47-08d03df8ff4a", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *这是一个简单的例子↓", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "db197868-f1d9-40af-a764-282df496553f": {"uid": "db197868-f1d9-40af-a764-282df496553f", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "301", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "这是摸头指令的测试事件，类型为指令前置\\n前提为：玩家触发的该指令\\n结算为：交互对象0号口上用flag增加1", "premise": {"sys_0": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A2_Flag|0_G_1": 1}}, "79f6e65f-36f6-45da-9d09-379469e9996d": {"uid": "79f6e65f-36f6-45da-9d09-379469e9996d", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "301", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "这是摸头指令的测试事件，类型为指令前置，内容为{TargetName}的头被摸秃了\\n前提为：玩家触发的该指令，交互对象的0号flag大于100\\n结算为：无", "premise": {"sys_0": 1, "CVP_A2_Flag|0_G_100": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b85a982f-d575-4fbc-a601-bfd8275431fc": {"uid": "b85a982f-d575-4fbc-a601-bfd8275431fc", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *当然，记得准备一个备忘录，记录每个flag的用途，避免你花半天去回想第7号flag是干什么用的来着", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "6263371c-7291-47f0-aacb-50620af3b05d": {"uid": "6263371c-7291-47f0-aacb-50620af3b05d", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "ca7a75de-e169-41d3-89da-8d1f1d5975f4": {"uid": "ca7a75de-e169-41d3-89da-8d1f1d5975f4", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*3.2 自定义指令", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "0f9b34e9-c5d3-4a49-84bd-89a1dc9358ae": {"uid": "0f9b34e9-c5d3-4a49-84bd-89a1dc9358ae", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *我想要个XXX的指令，但是游戏里没有，怎么办？", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "5ea76885-66df-4ebf-8a9b-5dabbe61fa16": {"uid": "5ea76885-66df-4ebf-8a9b-5dabbe61fa16", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *没错，编辑器连这种事情都做的到！甚至连代码都不用写！", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b496513d-8f5a-4ede-b259-7c7efb88e622": {"uid": "b496513d-8f5a-4ede-b259-7c7efb88e622", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *实现起来也非常简单，将指令选为[日常]-[角色特殊指令]，文本是三段式的\"指令名|指令耗时|指令文本\"", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "9e1167dd-6a6a-4ebb-b414-ae77c666e1de": {"uid": "9e1167dd-6a6a-4ebb-b414-ae77c666e1de", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *没了，就这样", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "1147b630-4511-420e-8df8-db70b890fcf6": {"uid": "1147b630-4511-420e-8df8-db70b890fcf6", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *下面是例子↓", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "b3f8de7b-26f8-47e3-b7e4-fab34bd84434": {"uid": "b3f8de7b-26f8-47e3-b7e4-fab34bd84434", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "5", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "自定义指令测试_A1|5|前提已满足，所以一定会出现的指令，对话经验+1", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A2_E|80_G_1": 1}}, "305a15ce-5725-438d-99d5-9031bb2ad124": {"uid": "305a15ce-5725-438d-99d5-9031bb2ad124", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "5", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "自定义指令测试_A2|5|前提无法满足，所以无法出现的指令，音乐经验+1", "premise": {"CVP_A2_F_L_0": 1, "CVP_A2_F_G_5": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A2_E|85_G_1": 1}}, "70466f8f-eeb2-4c4d-97e1-a8351f125431": {"uid": "70466f8f-eeb2-4c4d-97e1-a8351f125431", "adv_id": "999", "status_id": "5", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "自定义指令测试_A3|10|玩家展开了工作类指令时才会出现的指令，战斗经验+1", "premise": {"work_panel_show": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"CVE_A2_E|81_G_1": 1}}, "13b97391-431e-41ec-9cdb-16f13eb8fa28": {"uid": "13b97391-431e-41ec-9cdb-16f13eb8fa28", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *指令会在什么情况下可以被解锁使用，是由前提所决定的，前提不满足的指令会不出现，如A2", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "9e5f0708-3f07-4fc9-8799-2f9605f81813": {"uid": "9e5f0708-3f07-4fc9-8799-2f9605f81813", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *同时，还可以将指令归类到当前的指令类别面部中，如A3就限制为工作类指令", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "8d0a6f19-19b6-454e-a988-fb12f5370f2c": {"uid": "8d0a6f19-19b6-454e-a988-fb12f5370f2c", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*————————————分隔符————————————", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "3dd29c09-2e01-413f-bd27-e1d0462c190d": {"uid": "3dd29c09-2e01-413f-bd27-e1d0462c190d", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "*4.1 从哪里开始？", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "0e50836a-2eaf-41b2-8ab6-318d0a70dfe5": {"uid": "0e50836a-2eaf-41b2-8ab6-318d0a70dfe5", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *到这里的话，你应该已经掌握了事件编辑器的大部分功能了", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "6c41c70a-b73b-4df6-b280-af0cc9cc57d1": {"uid": "6c41c70a-b73b-4df6-b280-af0cc9cc57d1", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *很明显，事件编辑是口上编辑的完全上位替代，会让人觉得，一开始就用事件编辑形态不就好了吗", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "9ce5103a-98b8-48c5-9fd5-ed31d835359e": {"uid": "9ce5103a-98b8-48c5-9fd5-ed31d835359e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *虽然确实是这样，但是人总是需要一个学习和掌握的过程", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "7ced0948-7a3a-4278-8bae-46396366a9ed": {"uid": "7ced0948-7a3a-4278-8bae-46396366a9ed", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *你可以考虑把之前写过的口上，选取部分将其改造为更丰富的事件", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "5109eb1a-e21b-4701-bb3b-d21670844b2e": {"uid": "5109eb1a-e21b-4701-bb3b-d21670844b2e", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *也可以就把口上和事件分成两类东西，口上就写常见差分，事件就写特殊演出", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "36691998-2be3-4cf6-bcca-f53548e9ecd1": {"uid": "36691998-2be3-4cf6-bcca-f53548e9ecd1", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *总之，编辑器是自由的，你也是", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "3fe197eb-6630-4915-a8ff-17d84b8acad9": {"uid": "3fe197eb-6630-4915-a8ff-17d84b8acad9", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *另外，事件因为有了结算，所以如果错误地使用的话是会导致游戏BUG的", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "c5807d51-0c9e-407d-a30b-373f0824a821": {"uid": "c5807d51-0c9e-407d-a30b-373f0824a821", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *所以，多测试，不要嫌麻烦，虽然真的很麻烦，但是真的得多测试", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "6f98cc1a-10f8-475c-815f-1886defa5a52": {"uid": "6f98cc1a-10f8-475c-815f-1886defa5a52", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *另外的另外，多备份你的口上文件和事件文件，虽然也很麻烦，但是真的得做备份", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}, "a24b0be7-2ced-4c04-b13b-1f09d02ead20": {"uid": "a24b0be7-2ced-4c04-b13b-1f09d02ead20", "adv_id": "0", "status_id": "99", "start": 0, "type": 0, "text": "  *真的真的得备份", "premise": {"high_1": 1}, "settle": {}, "effect": {"9999": 1}}}